---
import Base from "../layouts/Base.astro";
---

<Base
  title="Shipping Policy — 8EyeTieDye"
  description="Shipping information for 8EyeTieDye orders including delivery times, costs, and international shipping."
>
  <section class="container mx-auto px-4 py-20 max-w-3xl">
    <h1
      class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold dye-gradient-text mb-8"
    >
      Shipping Policy
    </h1>

    <div class="prose prose-invert prose-lg space-y-6 text-gray-300">
      <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">Effective Date: March 21, 2026</p>

      <p>
        All 8EyeTieDye products are made to order using print-on-demand
        technology. Because each item is custom-printed with your unique AI
        design, please allow additional production time before shipping.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Production Time
      </h2>
      <p>
        Once your order is placed, your design is sent to our print partners for
        production. Typical production times are:
      </p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li>
          <strong>Apparel (tees, hoodies, leggings):</strong> 3–7 business days
        </li>
        <li><strong>Neckties:</strong> 5–10 business days</li>
      </ul>
      <p>
        Production times may vary during peak seasons or high demand periods.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Shipping Times
      </h2>
      <p>After production, shipping times depend on your location:</p>
      <ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-2">
        <li><strong>United States:</strong> 3–7 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Canada:</strong> 5–12 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Europe:</strong> 7–15 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Australia/New Zealand:</strong> 10–20 business days</li>
        <li><strong>Rest of world:</strong> 10–25 business days</li>
      </ul>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Total Delivery Estimate
      </h2>
      <p>
        Combining production and shipping, most US orders arrive within
        <strong>1–2 weeks</strong>. International orders may take
        <strong>2–4 weeks</strong>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Shipping Cost
      </h2>
      <p>
        Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on your location and
        order size. We ship to 20+ countries worldwide.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Order Tracking
      </h2>
      <p>
        Once your order ships, you'll receive a tracking number. You can track
        your order at any time by visiting your order page at
        <code>8eyetiedye.com/order/[your-order-id]</code>.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        Lost or Delayed Packages
      </h2>
      <p>
        If your package hasn't arrived within the estimated delivery window,
        please contact us at
        <a
          href="mailto:support@8eyetiedye.com"
          class="text-purple-400 hover:text-purple-300"
        >
          support@8eyetiedye.com
        </a>
        with your order ID, and we'll investigate with our shipping partner.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-2xl font-display font-bold text-white mt-10 mb-4">
        International Orders
      </h2>
      <p>
        International customers may be responsible for customs duties, taxes, or
        import fees charged by their country. These charges are not included in
        the product price or shipping cost and are the buyer's responsibility.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
